    Black Aracnia cackled with glee. Quickstrike had no surrendered. Armed 
with her bowcaster, and with the help of the internal autoguns, she made her 
way out of the bridge and to his position.
    "Ah, Quickstrike. Im sorry it has to be this way, but until we decide the 
fate of the Predacons, your my prisoner. Drop your....your cobra head gun and 
move to the brig. And dont try to run, the autoguns will bring you down in a 
seconed. March!" She ordered, pointing her bowcaster at his abdomen.
